                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d7">- <locus target="#26r">26r</locus> (incipit
                        page of the readings for the month Gǝnbot): coloured (red and black)
                        ornamental band; geometric motifs.</decoNote>
                     <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d8">- <locus target="#47r">47r</locus> (incipit
